<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.1">
<l>vāli māvalat toruvaṉa tuṭalkeṭa varicilai vaḷaivittaṉ</l>
<l>ṟēla nāṟutaṇ taṭampoḻi liṭampeṟa viruntanal limayattuḷ</l>
<l>āli māmuki latirtara varuvarai yakaṭuṟa mukaṭēṟi</l>
<l>pīli māmayiṉ ṉaṭañceyun taṭañcuṉaip</l>
<l>piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where Vāli, having once bent the striped bow</l>
<l rend="indent">so the body of the powerful one was destroyed,</l>
<l>Remained so to gain land in the cool wide groves scented with cardamom,</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti with wide ponds</l>
<l rend="indent">where the dark peacock with tail feathers does [its] dance,</l>
<l>Climbing the peak to reach the ridge of that rare mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">as dark rain clouds spontaneously thunder.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
